snippet.title: Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy:  Cloud Version - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Become Star-Lord and buckle up for a wild ride as you lead your band of misfits through an all-new story to become legendary heroes. You got this. Probably.

Marvel’s Guardians of the Galaxy: Cloud Version lands on Nintendo Switch 10/26! 

Learn more here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/marvels-guardians-of-the-galaxy-cloud-version-switch/
